.com&oh=00_AYBzbrhvpw_F9u-IuIQK5iTG_GZ2zPLfW7kohXuMTFLQxw&oe=6724BD3B"}, {"file_name": "6.png", "id": "556098763570189", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974900_556098766903522_8004750842823654047_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=NZerzZfqKUkQ7kNvgEhZoHs&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC52hYaWz2_kYHlKHP2LAt3W9KwHTjVcY_h2y65oTt2mA&oe=6724B86D"}, {"file_name": "3.png", "id": "9168495186528089", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974439_9168495206528087_4233145093264207487_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=FS3XA9lrT8sQ7kNvgFqafqd&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBzqFSKUrrcvHHiaFa2bINXHu7tUUGdfsfAc4yzYMVL6Q&oe=6724C2E2"}, {"file_name": "2.png", "id": "476003205442680", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982508_476003212109346_3995292706423684582_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=JckHxMtrlj0Q7kNvgGLSIP3&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCigsDKshU6hB2oYExaPsOwx_73p07XHGnopTZGyT8R-A&oe=6724D8E1"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Rogue Pi\u00f1atas: VRmageddon [DEMO]", "keywords": ["roguelike", "roguelite", "action", "multiplayer"], "long_description": "EXPERIENCE THE DEMO FOR ROGUE PINATAS: VRMAGEDDON!\n\nA multiplayer VR roguelite game. Your mission? Survive the party-apocalyptic world by bashing your way through swarms of invading Pi\u00f1atas, where every swing could mean survival or sweet defeat!\n\nGAME FEATURES:\n\n6 Characters to Choose: As one the few survivors, it's up to you to answer the call!\n\nWeapon Galore: Master over 150+ different combinations of attack through weapon evolutions and Dual Wielding.\n\nWorld-Ending Locations: From your local neighborhood to the treacherous desert, each area offers new dangers and opportunities for mayhem.\n\nCandy-packed Enemies: These pi\u00f1atas are somehow thinking, moving, and growing smart